# v5.6 Web UI with Flask
## 완전한 웹 애플리케이션: Flask + HTML/CSS + v5.5 API

![Status](https://img.shields.io/badge/status-complete-brightgreen)
![Framework](https://img.shields.io/badge/framework-Flask-blue)
![Frontend](https://img.shields.io/badge/frontend-HTML5%2FCSS3-orange)

